<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>I'm Sorry ❤️</title>

<style>
*{
margin:0;
padding:0;
box-sizing:border-box;
font-family:Arial,sans-serif;
}

body{
background:linear-gradient(135deg,#ff9ec4,#ffd6e8);
display:flex;
justify-content:center;
align-items:center;
height:100vh;
overflow:hidden;
}

.card{
background:white;
width:90%;
max-width:420px;
padding:30px;
border-radius:25px;
text-align:center;
box-shadow:0 15px 35px rgba(0,0,0,.2);
animation:fade 1.5s;
}

h1{
color:#ff3b7d;
font-size:32px;
margin-bottom:10px;
}

p{
font-size:18px;
color:#555;
line-height:1.7;
margin:20px 0;
}

button{
padding:15px 35px;
border:none;
border-radius:30px;
background:#ff3b7d;
color:white;
font-size:18px;
cursor:pointer;
transition:.3s;
}

button:hover{
transform:scale(1.05);
}

#hidden{
display:none;
margin-top:20px;
font-size:22px;
color:#ff3b7d;
font-weight:bold;
}

.heart{
position:absolute;
color:#ff4f88;
font-size:22px;
animation:float 8s linear infinite;
}

@keyframes float{
0%{
transform:translateY(100vh);
opacity:0;
}
20%{
opacity:1;
}
100%{
transform:translateY(-120vh);
opacity:0;
}
}

@keyframes fade{
from{
opacity:0;
transform:scale(.8);
}
to{
opacity:1;
transform:scale(1);
}
}
</style>

</head>

<body>

<div class="card">

<h1>I'm Sorry ❤️</h1>

<p>
I know I hurt you.<br><br>

There isn't a single excuse for my mistakes.

You deserve love, respect, and honesty.

If I could go back, I would change everything that caused you pain.

I miss your smile, your voice, and the happiness we shared.

I'm truly sorry from the bottom of my heart.

If you ever decide to give me one more chance...

I promise to love you better every single day.
</p>

<button onclick="showMessage()">Tap Here ❤️</button>

<div id="hidden">
Will you forgive me? 🥺❤️
</div>

</div>

<script>
function showMessage(){
document.getElementById("hidden").style.display="block";
}

function hearts(){
const heart=document.createElement("div");
heart.className="heart";
heart.innerHTML="❤️";
heart.style.left=Math.random()*100+"vw";
heart.style.fontSize=(20+Math.random()*30)+"px";
heart.style.animationDuration=(4+Math.random()*5)+"s";
document.body.appendChild(heart);

setTimeout(()=>{
heart.remove();
},9000);
}

setInterval(hearts,300);
</script>

</body>
</html>
